# secretmanager

This library provides access to the secretmanager API.

## Installation

```bash
go get example.com/secretmanager
```

## Usage

```go
import "secretmanager"

client := secretmanager.NewClient()
```

## APIs

- google/cloud/secretmanager/v1
- google/cloud/secretmanager/v1beta2
